## Architecture Changes in v0.2

1. **Coordinator + Parallel Workers**: All workers (papers, blogs, news+market) run in parallel
2. **Self-Contained Workers**: Each worker does fetch + enrich independently (no round-trips)
3. **Memory System**: briefing-memory/ with MEMORY.md index and topic files
4. **Skeptical Memory**: Memory treated as hints not truth, verified before use
5. **Coordinator Synthesis**: Coordinator reads ALL findings and synthesizes (not lazy delegation)


